reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Charges extremely fast. I liked you could choose the color also. Cord is longer than the one that comes with the iPhone. No issues and I’ve had it for a couple weeks now. All around great purchase. I’d suggest buying the package of two it’s better worth your money. Glad I bought the two so I can leave one at my house and one in my car.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good for the price
reviews.reviewText: These are nice little chargers but the reason I got them is because I needed something that would plug into my car but the cord is not a USB on the one end. Its fine because I can use them in my house. But I should have paid more attention when purchasing. They work perfectly fine but next time I'll make sure its a regular USB on the one end of the cord.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great product, charges phone fast!
reviews.reviewText: I've got to say, this iPhone Fast Charger 3 Pack has been a total game-changer for me. Finally, a charger that lives up to the "fast" in its name! As an Apple user, having that MFi certification is a must for me, and this set ticks that box. The 20W power delivery is no joke – it juices up my iPhone at lightning speed, which is a game-changer, especially when I'm in a rush.The fact that it comes in a pack of three is super convenient. I've got one in the bedroom, one in the living room, and another in my bag for on-the-go charging. No more searching for a charger when my battery is running low – these are strategically placed throughout my day-to-day life.The build quality is solid, and they don't feel like they'll fall apart after a few months of use. The USB-C connection is sturdy, and I haven't experienced any connectivity issues. The three-pack also makes it a great value for the price, considering the quality and fast-charging capability.One thing to note is that the charging cable could be a bit longer, but that's a minor gripe. If you're sitting close to an outlet, it's perfect, but for those times when you need a bit more reach, an extra foot would have been nice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars One cable went out after a month and a half
reviews.reviewText: The product works great. Looks and feels very high quality however one of the cables just stopped working after a month a half of normal use. I never snagged or pulled the cable, no water damage, outlets are grounded. I tested the cable on other charging devices but no luck. Now I have one cable left and two wall adapters that still work excellent. I would recommend the product as I believe I may have just gotten a faulty cable, idk.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly what I needed
reviews.reviewText: I previously had a nylon charger which worked for a while but because my outlet is at a weird angle, the charger cord was twisted when in use. As a result, the charger only lasted for a few months which was surprising because you think it would have been more durable. I have had this charger now for several months, same outlet but so far no problems. I ordered two and will order more to have on hand. I highly recommend this charger.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Fast charging, but sometimes doesn't work
reviews.reviewText: These are super cheap, and charge my iphone really fast. The only problem is that sometimes it just doesn't work. When it doesn't work I just have to flip the plug in part and it'll charge. Not a big deal but sometimes I plug it in thinking it'll charge but it's not. If this is the case, just make sure your phone is charging and it won't be a big deal. Kinda annoying tho
